data.description: WOW! Here is an opportunity that just can not be missed! Looking for your own country paradise? Look no further as this 4 Bedroom, 3 bath home, Nestled away on a secluded 5 acres is the one for you! Featuring a beautiful 3/4 wrap around deck, seclusion and endless possibilities! This Cape cod style home is the perfect country setting for you! Minute's away from Hanging Rock, Newley Purposed Equestrian center, Farm stores, Restaurants, Hiking, fishing, tubing down the river, and much more!
